<paragraph id="8BFAE50F4627FFA66ED7FF22FE96E6DA" blockId="5.[146,1128,155,214]" pageId="5" pageNumber="152">Die letztgenannte Pflanze wurde hier jedoch nicht gezielt angepflanzt sondern war verwildert.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BFAE50F4627FFA66ED7FEB8FEF0E716" blockId="5.[146,1021,257,452]" box="[146,372,257,282]" pageId="5" pageNumber="152">
<emphasis id="B931391D4627FFA66ED7FEB8FEF0E716" bold="true" box="[146,372,257,282]" pageId="5" pageNumber="152">Nahrungspflanzen</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BFAE50F4627FFA66ED7FE9AFCF4E730" blockId="5.[146,1021,257,452]" box="[146,880,291,316]" pageId="5" pageNumber="152">Eier und Raupen wurden an folgenden Pflanzenarten gefunden:</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BFAE50F4627FFA66ED7FEFCFDBFE752" blockId="5.[146,1021,257,452]" box="[146,571,325,350]" pageId="5" pageNumber="152">
<emphasis id="B931391D4627FFA66ED7FEFCFF18E752" box="[146,156,325,350]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="152">•</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C459E8C4627FFA66EEDFEFCFE3AE752" authority="(Stockrose)" baseAuthorityName="Stockrose" box="[168,446,325,350]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Alcea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="5" pageNumber="152" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rosea">
<emphasis id="B931391D4627FFA66EEDFEFCFEB4E752" box="[168,304,325,350]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="152">Alcea rosea</emphasis>
(Stockrose)
</taxonomicName>
: 34 Stellen
</paragraph>
